    "help.desc_iac": {
      "it": "Crea l'infrastruttura Azure per lo script (Resource Group, risorsa Foundry, Project, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Tre modalità via -IaCMode: generate (scrive provision.sh), dry-run (anteprima), execute (crea le risorse dopo conferma). Richiede Azure CLI.",
      "en": "Creates the Azure infrastructure for the script (Resource Group, Foundry resource, Project, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Three modes via -IaCMode: generate (writes provision.sh), dry-run (preview), execute (creates resources after confirmation). Requires Azure CLI.",
      "fr": "Crée l'infrastructure Azure pour le script (Resource Group, ressource Foundry, Projet, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Trois modes via -IaCMode : generate (écrit provision.sh), dry-run (aperçu), execute (crée les ressources après confirmation). Nécessite Azure CLI.",
      "es": "Crea la infraestructura de Azure para el script (Resource Group, recurso Foundry, Proyecto, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Tres modos con -IaCMode: generate (escribe provision.sh), dry-run (vista previa), execute (crea recursos tras confirmación). Requiere Azure CLI.",
      "pt": "Cria a infraestrutura Azure para o script (Resource Group, recurso Foundry, Projeto, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Três modos via -IaCMode: generate (escreve provision.sh), dry-run (prévia), execute (cria recursos após confirmação). Requer Azure CLI.",
      "de": "Erstellt die Azure-Infrastruktur für das Skript (Resource Group, Foundry-Ressource, Projekt, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Drei Modi über -IaCMode: generate (schreibt provision.sh), dry-run (Vorschau), execute (erstellt Ressourcen nach Bestätigung). Erfordert Azure CLI.",
      "ru": "Создаёт инфраструктуру Azure для скрипта (Resource Group, ресурс Foundry, проект, Log Analytics + Application Insights). Три режима через -IaCMode: generate (пишет provision.sh), dry-run (предпросмотр), execute (создаёт ресурсы после подтверждения). Требуется Azure CLI.",
      "zh": "为脚本创建 Azure 基础设施（资源组、Foundry 资源、项目、Log Analytics + Application Insights）。通过 -IaCMode 提供三种模式：generate（写入 provision.sh）、dry-run（预览）、execute（确认后创建资源）。需要 Azure CLI。",
      "ja": "スクリプト用の Azure インフラ（リソースグループ、Foundry リソース、プロジェクト、Log Analytics + Application Insights）を作成します。-IaCMode で 3 つのモード: generate（provision.sh を書き出し）、dry-run（プレビュー）、execute（確認後にリソース作成）。Azure CLI が必要です。",
      "hi": "स्क्रिप्ट हेतु Azure अवसंरचना बनाता है (Resource Group, Foundry संसाधन, Project, Log Analytics + Application Insights)। -IaCMode से तीन मोड: generate (provision.sh लिखता है), dry-run (पूर्वावलोकन), execute (पुष्टि के बाद संसाधन बनाता है)। Azure CLI आवश्यक।",
      "ar": "ينشئ بنية Azure التحتية للسكربت (مجموعة الموارد، مورد Foundry، المشروع، Log Analytics + Application Insights). ثلاثة أوضاع عبر ‎-IaCMode: ‏generate (يكتب provision.sh)، ‏dry-run (معاينة)، ‏execute (ينشئ الموارد بعد التأكيد). يتطلب Azure CLI."
    },
    "iac.dryrun_header": {
